item.title: CVE-2023-4270|2024-08-02T07:24:03.676Z -- unknown -- min%20max%20control
item.description: The Min Max Control WordPress plugin before 4.6 does not sanitise and escape a parameter before outputting it back in the page, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against high privilege users such as admin.
